overview.en: Blockchain Money Coin (JQB) is the world's first blockchain lending platform. It is a real platform for everyone to apply for loans. Moneycoin is a combination of exploring the blockchain world and the loan field. It is a loan trading platform based on blockchain technology and is also the use of all the “Changcoin” loan platform.
overview.zh: 区块链金钱币（JQB）是全球第一个区块链贷款平台，它是一个真正的人人都可以申请贷款的平台。金钱币是探索区块链世界与贷款领域的结合，是基于区块链技术的贷款交易平台，也是“驰币贷”贷款平台的一切使用通证。
